Archaeologists Find Ancient Mystery | Black Mountainside | New Thriller Movie

In the chilling mystery-thriller "Black Mountain Side," a team of archaeologists stumbles upon an enigmatic structure in the remote wilderness of Northern Canada, dating back over ten thousand years. As they delve deeper into this ancient finding, their communication systems mysteriously fail, leaving them cut off from the outside world. With isolation creeping in, the team starts to experience the unsettling effects of their solitude, blurring the lines between reality and the unknown.

2014.  Stars: Shane Twerdun, Michael Dickson, Carl Toftfelt
